{"id": "ChIJaYlVcgCBhYAR5IKYsf-rEAo", "rating": 4.2, "userRatingCount": 406, "displayName": {"text": "Parachute Bakery", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJaYlVcgCBhYAR5IKYsf-rEAo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xGbUxVc3ljM05GTTNZdGNWTnVWWE5tVUUxa2RsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Space is beautiful; staff is super friendly and pastries were on point. I especially loved the Gochujang Pimento Cheese Twist. We got there right when it opened and the line wasn’t too bad. I would skip the latte if you like ‘em strong.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Space is beautiful; staff is super friendly and pastries were on point. I especially loved the Gochujang Pimento Cheese Twist. We got there right when it opened and the line wasn’t too bad. I would skip the latte if you like ‘em strong.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Rachel Neiman", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104284268404830080293/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUOzzUIizNsMsmawrR0IGIl4NIVXhRYT0bULmAzn1LchoVXuvqB=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-31T02:54:32.385781001Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xGbUxVc3ljM05GTTNZdGNWTnVWWE5tVUUxa2RsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xGbUxVc3ljM05GTTNZdGNWTnVWWE5tVUUxa2RsRRAB!2m1!1s0x8085810072558969:0xa10abffb19882e4"}, {"name": "places/ChIJaYlVcgCBhYAR5IKYsf-rEAo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GRWEzbHFRbk5KY2xkalNqSmZRMEpvWkhScGMxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Such a beautiful bakery inside the Ferry Building! We tried a variety of pastries and drinks, and everything looked and tasted amazing. The pastries were flaky, fresh, and so pretty, with a great mix of sweet and savory options. The matcha and coffee were also really good. It’s a perfect spot to stop by with friends, share a box of pastries, and enjoy a cute bakery moment in San Francisco. Definitely worth visiting!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Such a beautiful bakery inside the Ferry Building! We tried a variety of pastries and drinks, and everything looked and tasted amazing. The pastries were flaky, fresh, and so pretty, with a great mix of sweet and savory options. The matcha and coffee were also really good. It’s a perfect spot to stop by with friends, share a box of pastries, and enjoy a cute bakery moment in San Francisco. Definitely worth visiting!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Julia tolikevideo", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103026817312905801102/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzCLMgf1eW_tJBKPqKPfFJQkRNBIirgJvn2b8igjgNAEUijcAO=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-02T21:13:10.166856012Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GRWEzbHFRbk5KY2xkalNqSmZRMEpvWkhScGMxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GRWEzbHFRbk5KY2xkalNqSmZRMEpvWkhScGMxRRAB!2m1!1s0x8085810072558969:0xa10abffb19882e4"}, {"name": "places/ChIJaYlVcgCBhYAR5IKYsf-rEAo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kQ04xcG9Wek5xYW5oVmFXWnliMU0zYzB3ek5FRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Absolutely worth the visit! Every pastry we tried was incredibly fresh, buttery, and perfectly flaky. You can really taste the quality and craftsmanship in every bite. The flavors were unique without being overly sweet, and everything looked just as amazing as it tasted. The staff was friendly, and the atmosphere in the Ferry Building made the experience even better. If you’re in San Francisco, this is a must-stop bakery. I’ll definitely be back!\nNaseer was Amazing!!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Absolutely worth the visit! Every pastry we tried was incredibly fresh, buttery, and perfectly flaky. You can really taste the quality and craftsmanship in every bite. The flavors were unique without being overly sweet, and everything looked just as amazing as it tasted. The staff was friendly, and the atmosphere in the Ferry Building made the experience even better. If you’re in San Francisco, this is a must-stop bakery. I’ll definitely be back!\nNaseer was Amazing!!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "aysha ali", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112591708473199829588/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ_EDwxF2dQoFbl0AuImRoram87oygXkp6hnjinHHpRc7UiYQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-29T02:50:56.323666963Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kQ04xcG9Wek5xYW5oVmFXWnliMU0zYzB3ek5FRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25kQ04xcG9Wek5xYW5oVmFXWnliMU0zYzB3ek5FRRAB!2m1!1s0x8085810072558969:0xa10abffb19882e4"}, {"name": "places/ChIJaYlVcgCBhYAR5IKYsf-rEAo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pJd05GcHBaMFp1Y1hWZlpISnlhMmx3TFRScE4yYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I got to try a couple of pastries thanks to a colleague who generously shared, and both were absolutely delicious. We had the strawberry crème croissant and the matcha Basque cheesecake.\n\nThe croissant was definitely my favorite: flaky, buttery, and filled with just the right amount of cream and strawberry. The matcha cheesecake was rich and balanced with a subtle earthy flavor. Together, the combo not only tasted amazing but looked so pretty too, almost too pretty to eat!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I got to try a couple of pastries thanks to a colleague who generously shared, and both were absolutely delicious. We had the strawberry crème croissant and the matcha Basque cheesecake.\n\nThe croissant was definitely my favorite: flaky, buttery, and filled with just the right amount of cream and strawberry. The matcha cheesecake was rich and balanced with a subtle earthy flavor. Together, the combo not only tasted amazing but looked so pretty too, almost too pretty to eat!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Louise", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100374130478832078121/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLeQbNttmfFJnYg9P8AdhgYMdX66mtxidj36uck_wmI75d8ZA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-07T16:02:09.166739815Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pJd05GcHBaMFp1Y1hWZlpISnlhMmx3TFRScE4yYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pJd05GcHBaMFp1Y1hWZlpISnlhMmx3TFRScE4yYxAB!2m1!1s0x8085810072558969:0xa10abffb19882e4"}, {"name": "places/ChIJaYlVcgCBhYAR5IKYsf-rEAo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGT2VHRlVYMVJtYjFSQ09FeHRSblpsY0VSYVptYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Made fresh daily with exceptional care and craftsmanship. I’m fortunate to live close by, but Parachute Bakery is absolutely worth a visit for anyone spending time in San Francisco.\n\nSignature pastries are available year-round alongside a rotating seasonal selection. Each pastry is beautifully executed and, more importantly, genuinely delicious. Prices also feel quite fair for the quality, and I love supporting small businesses that put this much care into what they do.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Made fresh daily with exceptional care and craftsmanship. I’m fortunate to live close by, but Parachute Bakery is absolutely worth a visit for anyone spending time in San Francisco.\n\nSignature pastries are available year-round alongside a rotating seasonal selection. Each pastry is beautifully executed and, more importantly, genuinely delicious. Prices also feel quite fair for the quality, and I love supporting small businesses that put this much care into what they do.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Michael Smith", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112642246246924670523/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJHv_oydNKofaNFFXjtZyjRu5kxYGmGy1wahMe4TddXvitRyA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-30T05:52:08.887552485Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGT2VHRlVYMVJtYjFSQ09FeHRSblpsY0VSYVptYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGT2VHRlVYMVJtYjFSQ09FeHRSblpsY0VSYVptYxAB!2m1!1s0x8085810072558969:0xa10abffb19882e4"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJaYlVcgCBhYAR5IKYsf-rEAo/photos/AWCwydgiGbUxZwbvVZKsFe1sy3Ke7nrZe4v01PbLCA-O9Hd6ABzR8tuBYWcs1WrDv4HewdSXYWBWEw_GTRq4sTsLoadiU2GdVxKcVHIarmAt-lPgS08nhfbzEN59GUHahKW7E6qF0y9nYZLJ7doNCc1qsDj2Xhofv8Pnsbr3Z5sslAVXiaIdiLaT-yVxSVa9pZbRKP0Qzl3QWWrYUzvgtpGpZp_IW7Fny58KoOgDm09L9z5G2VUiIXyu8uiDvfoLtFX6PK8kfTwP9RSavloVzz1G67QEIzC483d0_8tsiuBq9VDSUyMSS8Y1hh8cx1uElM6eWzy7iE5a31eDhksBuxt1HuLwRWYuWV1PeYhD1uwqr0IxZoCoLWcopirWnRvLAuKt0n9bCR0VvMtgEGJF_ygFr_aVCVLq1qxMaXL7M3QZKmK_ol2ke8K5A7rAI6ZXeFmG", "widthPx": 4800, "heightPx": 3200, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Parachute Bakery", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/113924895539509038177", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKcP0taK7pJZJdQsQeVjrS_UbQ5agDJoIOgVFk-pCFu5xUHBQ=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=!1e10!2sCIABIhCIPTZ8okwicNa9ni3Y__zY&t=27&cb_clien